  <summary date="2021-02-08T17:37:34Z" status="Introduced in House">Gun Trafficker Detection Act

This bill requires gun owners to report the theft or loss of a firearm to law enforcement. It imposes criminal penalties on a violator.

The bill also establishes a private right of action for a person injured by a firearm that is the subject of a violation.</summary>
